{
  "stem": "1858.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shortly before the war has ended, our factory was closed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, we did not know why.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't realize that the Allies were approaching.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the supplies to our factory could not be shipped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Therefore, slowly, they were closing up different sections of the factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What happened then, we were in the spring of 1945, we were forced to work in the fields building trenches.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But also working in fields, tilling the soil, and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was then that my sister became very ill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She had-- my sister, Mania, she had typhoid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Typhoid certainly meant death, for there was no medication to be gotten.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a sick room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And by that time, there was a Russian doctor in our camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was one of the Russian prisoners of war caught by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And since they would not place her in a men's camp, they brought her to our camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what could she do with two bare hands?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had no medication.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister was taken to the sick room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the nurse in the sick room was a girl from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After she was there a couple days, she told her and several other girls, tomorrow, you're going to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was when we still worked in the factory at the end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the morning, she dressed several of the girls and actually pushed them out into the hall, and they went to work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My sister could not perform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She lay in the back of the machine like a dead dog.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the girl--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't in the same building.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the girl who worked the machine next to hers was helping her, working the machines for her.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
